  _eventName: 'Refinery strikes: France faces fuel shortages'
  _date: September 21, 2024
  _subheading: For several days now, a series of strikes has been shaking up French
    refineries, seriously disrupting fuel production and distribution throughout
    the country. Initiated by unions to protest against working conditions and wage
    policies, these industrial actions have already led to shortages at many service
    stations.
  _coverImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 63e7cdb0f96db1612b9b3ce7e5ed8081, type: 3}
  _captionImage: Aenean malesuada gravida diam, non tempus eros elementum vel. Phasellus
